<newsItemPage guid="bf5c1e8a-2b1b-4175-aebe-2fbe989277a0" id="24761" nodeName="INGHAMS FREEZE PRICES AS A RESULT OF BREXIT" isDoc="" updated="2021-01-20T15:54:05.0670000Z" parentGUID="91b1da34-ae9e-4d24-b0ad-39b835023986" nodeTypeAlias="newsItemPage" templateAlias="NewsItemPage" sortOrder="1" published="false" isBlueprint="false">
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Wednesday, 29 June 2016, Godalming, UK-</strong> As a result of Britain voting to leave the European Union in last week’s referendum, Inghams has frozen all their summer and winter holiday prices, as well as committing to absorbing any currency, fuel or other cost increases and ruling out any surcharge once guests have booked.</p>
<p><strong>Paul Carter, Chief Operating Officer</strong> says, “The price freeze should alleviate uncertainty for those who have already booked, and gives prospective customers the advantage of booking with a stronger pre-referendum rates of exchange to get the most out of their holiday.”</p>
<p>“We advise customers to book their holiday as soon as possible and add on any additional extras such as ski hire, tuition and ski passes to avoid future price rises caused by Brexit.”</p>
<p><strong>LATEST DEALS:</strong><br /><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e}" title="Ski Holidays">Ski</a></strong><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> – from £889 per person – save £139 per person<br />Stay in the pretty village of Saas Fee, Switzerland which boasts perfectly groomed slopes for beginner and intermediate skiers, beautiful winter walking trails and the world’s highest revolving restaurant. Inghams is offering seven-nights on a half-board basis at the <a data-udi="umb://document/59460c7100664880a3f93ff191d15e13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59460c7100664880a3f93ff191d15e13}" title="Hotel Schweizerhof Gourmet &amp; Spa">4.5* Schweizerhof Gourmet and Spa hotel </a>from £889, saving £139, departing on 16 December 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Geneva and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="/{localLink:1065}" title="Ski Holidays">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><a href="/{localLink:c79fe667-b034-4936-b5d2-ba74cfe5e8b0}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays"><strong>Lakes and Mountains</strong> </a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b}" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm">Hinterglemm</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria</a>– from £499 per person – save £399 per person <br />Head for the rolling hills of the scenic Glemm Valley this summer, a paradise for hikers with over 400km of walking trails to explore and more than 30 rustic mountain huts dotted throughout the region. Available for all guests the Saalbach-Hinterglemm Joker Card gives unlimited use of all cable cars and buses in the valley, as well as free entrance to local attractions. Inghams is offering seven-nights on a catered basis at the <a data-udi="umb://document/a494f61fd0f7439caf630303ca0c83ad" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a494f61fd0f7439caf630303ca0c83ad}" title="Chalet Hotel Pinzgauerhof (Hinterglemm)">Chalet Hotel Pinzgauerhof </a>from £499pp, saving £399pp, departing on 20 July 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Salzburg and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit w<a href="/ww.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays">ww.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays</a> or call 01483 791 116.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e2861bb9ee6b4ce199a3d2ed421a8a97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e2861bb9ee6b4ce199a3d2ed421a8a97}" title="Kirchberg">Kirchberg</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria</a> – from £599 per person - save £449 per person<br />Located in Kirchberg, close to the pretty village of Kitzbühel, the boutique <a data-udi="umb://document/ed1ddb15096d44309ffbb9350248164a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed1ddb15096d44309ffbb9350248164a}" title="Relais &amp; Châteaux Rosengarten">5* Relais &amp; Châteaux Hotel Rosengarten</a> is the perfect retreat to escape everyday life and re-energise in the mountains. Combining sophisticated design and comfort, the hotel boasts an award winning restaurant, considered as one of the top gourmet spots in the Alps, as well as a modern leisure area with sauna, steam room and relaxation area, with a wide range of massage and beauty treatments. Inghams is offering seven-nights on a half-board basis at the 5* Relais &amp; Châteaux Hotel Rosengarten from £599pp, saving £449pp, departing 20 July 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Innsbruck and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays">www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays</a> or call 01483 791 116.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce}" title="Malcesine">Malcesine</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a> – from £459 per person - save £313 per person<br />The picturesque lakeside resort of Malcesine in Italy is the perfect base to explore Lake Garda, with its charming cafes and restaurants, cobbled street and historical buildings. Inghams is offering seven-nights, half-board accommodation at the <a data-udi="umb://document/a57ecfd85d9245b381ba6c90420e27ef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a57ecfd85d9245b381ba6c90420e27ef}" title="Hotel Cristallo">3* Hotel Cristallo</a> from £459pp, save £313pp, departing 9 July 2016. Price includes return flights from Bristol to Verona and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays">www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays</a> or call 01483 791 116.</p>
<p><br /><strong>Ends-</strong></p>
<p><strong>For press enquiries please contact:</strong><br />PR Executive, Lydia Crisostomo, Inghams on 01483 79 10 53 /<a href="/Lydia.crisostomo@inghams.co.uk%20">Lydia.crisostomo@inghams.co.uk </a><br />Assistant PR Executive, Rachel Gaston, 01483 79 10 45 /<a href="mailto:rachel.gaston@inghams.co.uk">rachel.gaston@inghams.co.uk</a></p>]]></bodyText>
